vmarkd.css.custom.markdownDescription:
Custom CSS injected into the editor webview. Applies live (no reload). Target Vditor classes such as `.vditor-reset`, e.g.:

```css
.vditor-reset { line-height: 1.7; }
.vditor-reset h1 { color: #6cb6ff; }
```

For stylesheet files instead, use `#vmarkd.css.external#`.
